78. Instruction Mix and Arithmetic Intensity
======================================================================

--- Instruction Throughput Comparison ---

| Operation | 4K | 16K | 64K | Relative Speed |
|----------|-----|------|------|----------------|
| Add | 0.05 | 0.15 | 0.58 | 0.26x |
| Mul | 0.04 | 0.15 | 0.57 | 0.97x |
