2. Shuffle Down/Up have ~same cost, choice depends on data flow
3. Broadcast is most efficient for sharing single value
4. Avoid sequential communication patterns in warp (31x overhead)
5. Warp-level primitives enable efficient parallel algorithms
6. Use simd_shuffle_xor with masks like 16,8,4,2,1 for reductions

